# Operations Center: Orders, Payments & Customer Module
## Complete Technical Documentation Pack
### Odoo POS Cafe | MERN Stack | Tailwind CSS | MongoDB Atlas | Hackathon Final Round

---

> **Module Status**: Production-Ready  
> **Stack**: React 18 + Vite, Node.js + Express, MongoDB Atlas, Tailwind V3  
> **Security Guarding**: Complete (JWT Auth + Deep RBAC Matrix + Query/Action Restrictions)  
> **Design Continuity**: Passed (Premium Light-Mode Ivory/Cafe palette match)

