## 4. Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) Matrix

Security is physically enforced at three tiers:
1. **Frontend Router Check:** Prevents physical payload loads of components.
2. **Frontend UI Manipulation:** Strips buttons or conditional tools (e.g. Delete button removed from Cashier).
3. **Backend Middleware Enforcement:** Will throw 403 on API interactions from bypassed clients.

| Feature Area | Operations | Manager / Admin | POS / Cashier | Kitchen | Customer |
| --- | --- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---: |
| **System Access** | Access `/operations` Route | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **System Access** | API Interception Validation | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (403) | ❌ (403) |
| **Orders Menu** | View all historical orders | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Orders Menu** | Select/View single order details | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Orders Menu** | Archive bulk orders | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Orders Menu** | Delete draft orders permanently | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Payments** | View generalized payment list | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Payments** | View aggregated metric blocks | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Customers** | View customer directory | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Customers** | Search matching parameters | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Customers** | Quick-Create new profiles | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| **Customers** | Override physical profile metadata | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |

